                },
                {
                    "text": " waking up early after summer break"
                }
            ],
            "tips": "Always followed by a noun OR -ing verb: 'get used to school' or 'get used to waking up early'. Never + base verb."
        },
        {
            "word": "come along",
            "wordType": "phrasal verb",
            "definition": [
                {
                    "text": "To "
